@startuml
title レストランシステム - コンポーネント図

package "Web Layer" {
  [index.php] as Web
}

package "Domain Layer" {
  [User Class] as User
  [Employee Class] as Employee
  [Company Class] as Company
  [RestaurantLocation Class] as Location
  [RestaurantChain Class] as Chain
}

package "Interface Layer" {
  [FileConvertible Interface] as Interface
}

package "Data Generator" {
  [Random Data Generator] as Generator
}

package "Output Formatters" {
  [HTML Formatter] as HTML
  [Markdown Formatter] as Markdown
  [Array Formatter] as Array
}

Web --> Chain : 生成・表示
Web --> Generator : データ生成依頼

Chain --> Location : 管理
Location --> Employee : 管理
Employee --|> User : 継承

User ..|> Interface : 実装
Employee ..|> Interface : 実装
Company ..|> Interface : 実装
Chain ..|> Interface : 実装

Interface --> HTML : 変換
Interface --> Markdown : 変換
Interface --> Array : 変換

Generator --> Chain : ランダムデータ生成

@enduml
